snippet: Devin Booker and Willie Cauley-Stein each scored 15 points and top-ranked Kentucky shook off the shock of losing junior forward Alex Poythress by rolling past No. 21 North Carolina 84-70 on Saturday....

headline.print_headline: No. 1 Kentucky Rolls No. 21 North Carolina
headline.main: No. 1 Kentucky Rolls No. 21 North Carolina

lead_paragraph: Devin Booker and Willie Cauley-Stein each scored 15 points and top-ranked Kentucky shook off the shock of losing junior forward Alex Poythress by rolling past No. 21 North Carolina 84-70 on Saturday.
